Title: Redemption (2)
Plot: Carter must find a way to save Earth from total destruction at the hands of the Goa'uld, who have turned the Stargate into a doomsday bomb. Rya'c joins his father on a mission to destroy the Goa'uld weapon.
GuestStars: Dale Hall, Ivan Cermak, Robert Thurston, Robert Clarke, Michael Soltis, Grizz Salzl, Craig McNair, Tobias Mehler, Aleks Paunovic, Gary Chalk, David Hewlett, Christopher Kennedy
